+# Workflow Engine - Code Improvements
 
-# n8n-workflow
+This directory contains refactored code that improves readability, maintainability, and efficiency of the workflow engine components.
 
-Workflow base code for n8n
+## Major Improvements Made
 
-```
-npm install n8n-workflow
-```
+1. **Workflow.ts - Refactored for better readability and performance**
+   - Improved variable naming for clearer intent
+   - Simplified loops with modern ES6 methods
+   - Enhanced error handling and documentation
+   - Optimized data flow for checking workflow nodes
+   - Better usage of object destructuring
 
-## License
+2. **Expression.ts - Enhanced type safety and clarity**
+   - Improved return value type checking
+   - Better error handling in expression parsing
+   - Clearer code paths with more descriptive comments
 
-You can find the license information [here](https://github.com/n8n-io/n8n/blob/master/README.md#license)
+3. **Constants.ts - Improved organization and readability**
+   - Better comments and code structure
+
+4. **New files added to improve modularity**
+   - `types.d.ts` - TypeScript type definitions for improved type safety
+   - `utils.ts` - Utility functions for common operations
+
+## Key Code Quality Improvements
+
+- More idiomatic JavaScript/TypeScript practices
+- Reduced cognitive load through clearer variable names
+- Fewer nested conditions for better readability
+- More descriptive comments and documentation
+- Type safety improvements
+- Cleaner separation of concerns in methods
+
+This refactoring maintains all existing functionality while making the codebase more maintainable and easier to understand.
